metadata.name: that, but he also sold the house
metadata.description:
in the city, and used it all to buy fodder for those things. It is said that because of this, his father was made ill.



Wang Xian drove his tricycle full of goods through the village. After five or six minutes, he came to a building surrounded by high walls of about three meters, with only one iron gate.



At the moment, in front of the iron gate, stood two middle-aged people.



Seeing these two people, Wang Xian's face changed slightly.
